47 GeneratePose::GeneratePose(const std::string& name) : MonitoringGenerator(name) {
48  auto& p = properties();
49  p.declare<geometry_msgs::PoseStamped>("pose", "target pose to pass on in spawned states");
50 }

52 void GeneratePose::reset() {
53  upstream_solutions_.clear();
54  MonitoringGenerator::reset();
55 }

57 void GeneratePose::onNewSolution(const SolutionBase& s) {
58  // It's safe to store a pointer to this solution, as the generating stage stores it
59  upstream_solutions_.push(&s);
60 }
61 
62 bool GeneratePose::canCompute() const {
63  return !upstream_solutions_.empty();
64 }
65 
66 void GeneratePose::compute() {
67  if (upstream_solutions_.empty())
68  return;
69 
70  planning_scene::PlanningScenePtr scene = upstream_solutions_.pop()->end()->scene()->diff();
71  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped target_pose = properties().get<geometry_msgs::PoseStamped>("pose");
72  if (target_pose.header.frame_id.empty())
73  target_pose.header.frame_id = scene->getPlanningFrame();
74  else if (!scene->knowsFrameTransform(target_pose.header.frame_id)) {
75  ROS_WARN_NAMED("GeneratePose", "Unknown frame: '%s'", target_pose.header.frame_id.c_str());
76  return;
77  }
78 
79  InterfaceState state(scene);
80  state.properties().set("target_pose", target_pose);
81 
82  SubTrajectory trajectory;
83  trajectory.setCost(0.0);
84 
85  rviz_marker_tools::appendFrame(trajectory.markers(), target_pose, 0.1, "pose frame");
86 
87  spawn(std::move(state), std::move(trajectory));
88 }

91 } // namespace moveit
